Name: PASSABILITY
Explanation: DEFINES THE DEGREE OF DIFFICULTY IN PASSING OVER OR AROUND AN AREA OF GROUND OR OBJECT.

Name: HAZARD PASSABILITY
Explanation: DEFINES THE DEGREE OF DIFFICULTY IN PASSING AROUND A HAZARD.

Name: WEATHER RELATED ROUTE CONDITIONS
Explanation: PROVIDES CODES FOR DESCRIBING THE PASSABILITY OF A ROUTE CONSIDERING THE IMPACT OF WEATHER ON THAT ROUTE.
